title: Dr. Tannaz Mokhtari, ND
description: Metabolic Balance Naturópata asesor Dr. Tannaz Mokhtari, ND cerca Vaughan
text:
Hi!
I am a Naturopathic Doctor practicing in Richmond Hill/Vaughan area with a specific focus on Menopause and Hormone changes. As a Metabolic Balance coach, I find this program to be an amazing and important tool in helping individuals balance their metabolism, loose weight and feel great.
I am passionate about Empowering individuals to obtain their health goals!
I provide virtual visits as well as in person visits.
Please visit www.your-nd.com for bookings and more information.
